{"tid":392124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剝智慧齒簡直係人生一大爽事！","createTime":"2017-09-08T09:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T09:49:26.000Z","uid":59870,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d9d3cf510184642bc1321dd04dede66a0b5229","tid":392124,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"之前QE照X光話我下面兩隻牙90度打橫生(深藏係牙肉同骨入面冇露過頭) 隻牙根痴住神經線咁生 問我剝唔剝 但佢話我呢啲case好易整傷神經線搞到下巴/下唇以後冇知覺 咁我聽到緊係唔剝啦 又冇痛過 但後尾諗做完電療有5年(大概)係冇牙醫夠膽同你剝牙 利申22歲生緊鼻咽癌三期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就把心一橫決定剝撚曬四隻   星期二話我想剝 星期五就幫我剝 聽講呢政府醫院呢啲起碼要排一兩年<br />\n<br />\n打全身麻醉訓左唔知幾耐醒返就搞掂 而家過左6個鐘都未痛 只係有小小脹嘅感覺 亦都萬幸冇整到神經線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望今晚唔好痛 我仲要做抗癌勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一世唔洗煩智慧齒嘅感覺真係好撚爽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af485b11799f76a5eefacd5815f2801a512d24d","tid":392124,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過一次四隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9d9ac5f93b728b36481124b70691a21e25e693","tid":392124,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}